n國際知名犬隻行為治療師<br />\n亞洲最佳犬隻行為治療師<br />\n國家地理頻道《金牌馴狗師：亞洲接班人》第二季<br />\n奇妙電視節目《煉狗術師》主持<br />\n有線電視節目《寵物狗救星》主持及《寵物ER - 寵物襲地球》等<br />\n超水準犬隻訓練技巧獲《超級馴犬師》美喻<br />\nEric 與愛犬 Teeny「人狗減肥操」短片於全球網上總數錄得超過1億點擊率及數百萬個「讚好」。<br />\n香港保護遺棄動物協會(SAA)犬隻訓練顧問<br />\n香港保護遺棄動物協會(SAA)領犬員訓練課程導師<br />\n聖雅各福群會-特寵部隊Pet Troop計劃犬隻訓練導師<br />\n澳洲犬隻訓練師學校認可犬隻訓練師 (CIC, Dog Trainer School, Australia)<br />\n曾任澳洲墨爾本Blue Cross Animals Shelter 義務犬隻訓練員<br />\n澳洲認可犬隻訓練師(Dog Obedience Guidance System of Australia)<br />\n澳洲犬隻訓練師協會會員(Australian Association of Professional Dog Trainers)<br />\n澳洲墨爾本Blue Cross Animals Shelter 義務犬隻訓練師<br />\n多年犬隻練習場及上門犬隻訓練經驗"},{"pid":"3f5e72fc8bf4364b96f403b6baabc0216669743c","tid":480784,"uid":33825,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5b285aec2f8e04f9a4173a580049288a56c3b054","tid":480784,"uid":71062,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5e317cccb9706f3b11c14a1b63831456d24991c2","tid":480784,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T15:51:21.000Z","msg":"做緊第二季喇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T14:19:45.000Z","msg":"佢教狗好勁，唔打唔鬧都教到D狗勁聽話"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T17:22:07.000Z","msg":"真係好勁 我都係呢幾日先睇<br />\n好佩服佢 特別係第一季第三集<br />\n兩隻東德牧羊犬打架個陣 Eric沖去制止真係好撚有型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abe4ab5919d6c221b2b6637f623cce33d729a967","tid":480784,"uid":71062,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3f5e72fc8bf4364b96f403b6baabc0216669743c","tid":480784,"uid":33825,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5b285aec2f8e04f9a4173a580049288a56c3b054","tid":480784,"uid":71062,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5e317cccb9706f3b11c14a1b63831456d24991c2","tid":480784,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T15:51:21.000Z","msg":"做緊第二季喇"},"c